data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value: _ Users need to have a account and login user interface. _ Connecting to the machine by selecting com on Connection page. _ Set up machine by selecting mode, time, level on Set up page. _ With Manual mode, Users can control machine on Controller page (not be available for Auto mode). _ Users can provise status of machine like battery value, time up,..on Status page.

data.name: richTextBox2.Text
data.value: _ Be a newest version designed by Tuan nguyen & My Duyen in 2019. _ Has some special functions comparing to old generation vacuum cleaner. _ Save time, effort, battery. _ Has 2 mode Auto, Manual help user have more flexibility in control. _ ...
